oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 13th Annual Nashville Hobby and Craft Christmas Market
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Christmas; Fairs; Holidays; Woodcuts (prints);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Three color half sheet (black, red and green on white) announcing 13th Annual Nashville Hobby and Craft Christmas Market at the Tennessee State Fairgrounds on December 7, 8, 14, and 15. Poster features woodcuts of holly leaves. Poster was printed for job no. 1309. To view the paperwork for this order, see https://digi.countrymusichalloffame.org/digital/collection/hatch3/id/32542.
